Change history of abc nedit macro
=================================

Version 1.4
-----------

 - new menu entry "preview current tune"
   even in this case "goto error" works!

Version 1.3
-----------

 - new menu entries for interactive option setting
 - new menu entry "insert Header"
 - "Goto Error" only selects error instead of entire line
 - [1 [2 :: added to syntax highlighting

Version 1.2
-----------

 - new menu entries:
    o comment out region
    o uncomment region

Version 1.1
-----------

 - syntax highlighting
    o correction Info line 
 - macros
    o "...^" removed in message box
      (was confusing with proportional font)

Version 1.0
-----------

 - first creation with features:
    o abc syntax highlighting
    o two menu entries in the "Macro" menu
       + abc - Preview
       + abc - Goto Voice/Bar
